    "content": "Sisqo\r\nUnleash The Dragon\r\nThong Song\r\nTabbed By: Ben Gonzales \r\n  \r\n[tab]G:------------------------| \r\nD:------------------------| \r\nA:------------------------| \r\nE:--5--7--9------9--7--5--| [/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]Listen because it switches to this:\r\nG:------------------------| \r\nD:------------------------| \r\nA:------------------------| \r\nE:--6--8--10----10--8--6--| [/tab]\r\n\r\nHard isn't it?  Just add a couple of duh duhs and dun duns and listen\r\nto the song for those.  And there are a couple of places that there is\r\nno bass!  So you have to listen..  Otherwise, sounds good to me.",
